<br>•	Aptitude written test online
<br>•	Technical interview
<br>•	HR interview
    
<h5 class="card-title">Apple Registration Process:</h5>
<br>•	To Apply for Apple job openings or vacancies, candidates need to open the official company website www.apple.com.
<br>•	Click on careers page to see the available jobs.
<br>•	Click on the suitable job opening which suits your profile ( based on your qualification, experience).
<br>•	Read the job description and job role carefully.
<br>•	Click on the apply link to apply for the job opening.
<br>•	You need to login to apply for the vacancy. If you haven’t signed up yet, need to sign up first and then login.
<br>•	Fill all the required details and submit the application for further process.


 
